"""
actual-ecommerce-noter - Update Actual Budget transaction notes with Amazon or PayPal order details

This script correlates transaction records from CSV exports (Amazon or PayPal) with
transactions in Actual Budget, then updates the Notes field with purchase details.

Usage:
    actual-ecommerce-noter [--dry-run [json] | --execute] [--days X] [--force] [--format amazon|paypal|auto]
        [--actual-http-api URL | --actual-http-api-file /path/to/URLfile]
        [--actual-http-api-key SecretKey | --actual-http-api-key-file /path/to/SecretKey]
        [--actual-syncid SyncID | --actual-syncid-file /path/to/SyncID]
        File.csv File2.csv ...
"""

